```
<div class="block">
  <div class="s-label">01 · Background</div>
  <div class="s-title">The need</div>
  <div class="s-body">
    Every time a buyer discovers a product in a conversation, a video, or an AI chat — the moment they want to buy, the experience breaks. They are thrown into a checkout page, a UPI app, another screen. The conversation ends. The friction begins.
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sep"></div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="s-label">02 · Problem Statement</div>
  <div class="s-title">What's broken</div>
  <div class="s-body">
    Razorpay, UPI, Zomato all pivoted to agentic payments — <strong>right direction, same flaw.</strong> Every merchant needs a custom integration. Every pilot is siloed. No agent can complete a payment safely and autonomously across merchants at scale. There is no standard.
  </div>
  <div class="tags">
    <span class="tag red">Siloed per merchant</span>
    <span class="tag red">Closed pilots</span>
    <span class="tag red">Conversation breaks at checkout</span>
    <span class="tag red">No open standard</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sep"></div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="s-label">03 · Solution</div>
  <div class="s-title">ShopLens on UCP + Samsung APIs</div>
  <div class="s-body">
    Google launched <strong>UCP in January 2026</strong> — an open protocol for AI agents to transact with any merchant. ShopLens is built on it. The AI detects products, holds a full multi-turn conversation, and the agent completes the payment securely using <strong>Samsung's SingleStore and Single Checkout APIs</strong> — entirely within the chat. No redirects. No forms. No UPI switch.
  </div>
  <div class="tags">
    <span class="tag dark">Google UCP</span>
    <span class="tag dark">SingleStore</span>
    <span class="tag dark">Single Checkout</span>
    <span class="tag teal">YOLOv8 · CLIP</span>
    <span class="tag teal">LangChain · Ollama</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sep"></div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="s-label">05 · Why AI Only</div>
  <div class="ai-box">
    <p>
      <strong>Intent understanding</strong> — LLM interprets multi-turn shopping dialogue, resolves ambiguity, extracts preference across a full conversation. No rule engine can do this.<br/><br/>
      <strong>Autonomous payment execution</strong> — agent handles authentication, order creation, and payment via Samsung APIs without human intervention. Requires reasoning, not scripting.<br/><br/>
      <strong>Visual product detection</strong> — CLIP + YOLOv8 bridge the gap between what a camera sees and what a merchant sells — impossible without AI.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
